# SQL Day 1

## CREATE DATABASE

CREATE DATABASE college;

Purpose:
Creates a new database.

---

## USE DATABASE

USE college;

Purpose:
Selects the database.

---

## CREATE TABLE

CREATE TABLE Student(
    ID INT,
    Name VARCHAR(50),
    Marks INT
);

Purpose:
Creates Student table.

---

## INSERT INTO

INSERT INTO Student VALUES
(1,'Nikitha',95);

Purpose:
Adds data to table.

---

## SELECT

SELECT * FROM Student;

Purpose:
Displays all columns.

---

## WHERE

SELECT * FROM Student
WHERE ID = 1;

Purpose:
Filters rows.

---

## UPDATE

UPDATE Student
SET Marks = 100
WHERE Name = 'Tanya';

Purpose:
Modifies existing data.

---

## DELETE

DELETE FROM Student
WHERE Name = 'Rahul';

Purpose:
Removes data.
